00:28:10.285 --> 00:28:11.160
You won't believe it.

00:28:11.160 --> 00:28:12.201
You got to come see this.

00:28:12.201 --> 00:28:16.590
So he had this crazy,
new thing in 1977.

00:28:16.590 --> 00:28:19.080
