00:37:03.040 --> 00:37:05.290
the earth goes around the
sun instead of the other way

00:37:05.290 --> 00:37:06.300
around.

00:37:06.300 --> 00:37:09.800
Or Galileo-- I know the moon
looks like a perfect circle,

00:37:09.800 --> 00:37:12.880
but if you take this telescope,
you can see it's full of bumps.

00:37:12.880 --> 00:37:14.630
Well, we're going to
have to imprison you.

00:37:14.630 --> 00:37:16.040
I know.

00:37:16.040 --> 00:37:17.950
