continually being innovated,

00:47:47.540 --> 00:47:51.920
being modified and improved
and made more effective.

00:47:51.920 --> 00:47:54.650
And the big thing
nominally, until recently,

00:47:54.650 --> 00:47:57.470
the big thing was to have
cool weapons, not use them.

00:47:57.470 --> 00:47:59.540
And that was the big idea.

00:47:59.540 --> 00:48:04.320
But it's getting weird, peoples.

00:48:04.320 --> 00:48:06.170
It's getting weird.

00:48:06.170 --> 00:48:10.790
