I grew up with
the space program.

00:50:32.290 --> 00:50:34.270
People my age had
the space program.

00:50:34.270 --> 00:50:38.505
So science was imbued,
was embedded, in society.

00:50:38.505 --> 00:50:41.080
It was just part of
what went on every day,

00:50:41.080 --> 00:50:44.440
along with this crazy optimism
that science scientists

00:50:44.440 --> 00:50:46.060
and engineers could
solve any problem.

00:50:46.060 --> 00:50:47.470
We're going to go to the moon.

00:50:47.470 --> 00:50:49.120
